data.description: Great opportunity awaits you.  THIS great space is   rarely offered. You will enjoy entertaining in this 2400 square foot  two car garage colonial home. This spacious home is  complete with  New roof  and  a  3/4 finished basement all  tucked away on a quite cul-de- sac in the Pheasant Walk community of Newtown Grant.  This open floor plan is easy to navigate.   Once inside you can move effortlessly from  room to room including the first floor library.  Hard wood floors compliment the living room ,  formal dining room eat in island kitchen and more.  Over look the warm family room from the eat in kitchen. Enjoy the roar of the fireplace in the open and airy striking vaulted ceiling completing the cozy family room .  The Main bedroom has its own spacious private main bathroom and roman tub. Easy access to all the bedrooms and the large hallway bath room .   Entertain on rear patio, basement, family room and more.  See this home soon . This may just be your holiday gift to yourself if you have been waiting for this neighborhood.  Agents please see private showing remarks.  :)
